Executives from all parties including CPI(M) state committee member K.Kamaraj, S.Muthukannan, CPI (M) secretary, Tirupur district, M.Ravi, CPI secretary, Tirupur district, Ramasamy of Congress party, and Sampath from the MDMK, all took part in the agitation.
